column2: Ramaiah Memorial Hospital  is looking for Laparoscopic Surgeon  to join our dynamic team and embark on a rewarding career journey     A Laparoscopic Surgeon is a medical professional specializing in minimally invasive surgical procedures using laparoscopic technology     Their tasks may include performing laparoscopic surgeries, such as cholecystectomy, appendectomy, and hernia repair, using small incisions and specialized instruments, evaluating patient conditions and medical histories, collaborating with other healthcare professionals, and ensuring that proper surgical techniques and procedures are followed to ensure patient safety and optimal outcomes     They should have extensive knowledge of laparoscopic techniques and technologies, as well as strong clinical skills and decision-making abilities       ?
